flowchart TD
  A[IoT Device] -->|HTTP POST /events| B[Ingestion Module]
  B -->|Validate payload + API key| C[Redis Stream events:ingest]
  B -->|Emit| R1[event.received]

  C -->|Consumer Group XREADGROUP| D[Processor Worker]

  D --> E{Dedup check\nRedis SET NX EX}
  E -->|Duplicate| X1[ACK + Drop]
  E -->|Unique| F{Ordering policy}
  F -->|Stale delayed event| X2[Emit event.dropped + ACK]
  F -->|Accept| G[Persist EventLog in PostgreSQL]

  G --> H[Update Redis State]
  H --> H1[Sorted Set readings]
  H --> H2[Last seen timestamp]
  H --> H3[Aggregates avg/max/spikes]

  H --> I[Load active rules]
  I --> J[Rule Engine JSON DSL]
  J --> J1[Count window]
  J --> J2[Time window]
  J --> J3[Heartbeat missing]

  J --> K{Rule matched?}
  K -->|No| L[ACK stream event]
  K -->|Yes| M[Actions Module]

  M --> N[Create Alert in PostgreSQL]
  M --> O[Webhook call retry 1s to 2s to 4s]
  M --> P[Idempotency via dedupeKey]
  N --> R2[Emit alert.created]
  H2 --> R3[Emit device.status]

  L --> R4[Emit event.processed]
  D -->|Periodic check| J3

  R1 --> UI[Frontend Dashboard]
  R2 --> UI
  R3 --> UI
  R4 --> UI
